amstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4162350/extras/499a746c82e4c436de0f3bdde44e74dd.poster.avif?t=1774328505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4162350/extras/499a746c82e4c436de0f3bdde44e74dd.webm?t=1774328505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4162350/extras/499a746c82e4c436de0f3bdde44e74dd.mp4?t=1774328505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8 heroines \\ 8 temperaments.</strong> A strict head maid, a sincere laundress, a playful chef, a thrill-seeking lady, the lady of the house, and more - each with her own rules and weaknesses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4162350/extras/620596472ee4077538060f7723b17a3e.poster.avif?t=1774328505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4162350/extras/620596472ee4077538060f7723b17a3e.webm?t=1774328505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4162350/extras/620596472ee4077538060f7723b17a3e.mp4?t=1774328505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover the secrets of the mansion</strong>, discover the secrets of its inhabitants by peeping on them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a <strong>variety of fetishes and sex scenes</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are <strong>several endings</strong> waiting for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4162350/extras/d6ee93e31e6d420989e604d37d6